# This project needs no secrets to build or run — all tournament data is
# committed in src/data.ts, and the one data-refresh script
# (scripts/fetch-worldcup26.ts) uses the free, no-auth worldcup26.ir API.
#
# DISABLE_HMR (optional): set to "true" to turn off Vite hot-module reload
# and use polling-based file watching instead (useful in some sandboxes).
# DISABLE_HMR="true"
